{"tid":2215421,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"女友街頭遭咸豬手 男友捉色狼互毆同被捕","createTime":"2020-09-24T03:47:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T04:19:01.000Z","uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a3339348449b6bf7c759c978b4d9aa7e9be30e7c","tid":2215421,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T03:47:20.000Z","msg":"This is Hong Kong<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尖沙嘴一對情侶凌晨零時許行經金馬倫道及加拿分道交界時，28歲女友被一名男子非禮，男子即時沿加拿分道往堪富利士道方逃去。<br />\n<br />\n27歲姓張男友即時喝停男子並追截，在交界位爭執互毆。途人以為發生打鬥於是報案。警員趕到，以涉嫌非禮拘捕該名47歲姓梁男子，他受輕傷，與同樣受傷的男友分別送院治理，兩人同時涉嫌普通襲擊被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ukvXiJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ukvXiJ.png&h=f5466dee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9e17fa064d6489862d5e7578eb3215341483395","tid":2215421,"uid":326897,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T03:53:33.000Z","msg":"如果非禮係27歲嗰個，<br />\n47廢中分分鐘有好市民獎"},{"pid":"9b7b4e5840596be00549dca13055f9a5f7299042","tid":2215421,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T03:53:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97cf31b4090b736492e610ae16ae7900b5336e54","tid":2215421,"uid":7369,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T03:54:59.000Z","msg":"邊個係藍絲可以走先"},{"pid":"09fa902c68873ca7fe70306e6d22770b0d19cf30","tid":2215421,"uid":128600,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b9e17fa064d6489862d5e7578eb3215341483395","tid":2215421,"uid":326897,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T03:53:33.000Z","msg":"如果非禮係27歲嗰個，<br />\n47廢中分分鐘有好市民獎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T03:56:06.000Z","msg":"47廢中一比人捉到時一叫對方&ldquo;廢青，暴徒！亂港！&rdquo;<br />\n已經有popo 送上的士離開啦"},{"pid":"152da11e9c51b0ddfbcf7d60316d2d5f53559cf2","tid":2215421,"uid":57431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T03:57:54.000Z","msg":"打左格你話係47/48歲我都信<img src=\"/assets/face